OL,3,CWhat does the new Troubles legacy
OL,4,Cframework include?
OL,6,FA new UK and Irish deal on mechanisms
OL,7,Fto deal with the Northern Ireland
OL,8,FTroubles offers an opportunity to deal
OL,9,Fwith the "unfinished business" of the
OL,10,Fregion's peace agreement, Hilary Benn
OL,11,Fhas said .
OL,13,FThe Northern Ireland Secretary was
OL,14,Fjoined by Tanaiste Simon Harris at
OL,15,FHillsborough Castle on Friday
OL,16,Fafternoon to formally unveil the
OL,17,Fframework, which has been developed
OL,18,Ffollowing substantive engagement
OL,19,Fbetween the two governments following
OL,20,Fyears of impasse over the toxic legacy
OL,21,Fof the conflict.
