OL,3,CWhat does the new Troubles legacy
OL,4,Cframework include?
OL,6,FMr Harris described the framework as a
OL,7,F"night and day improvement" on the
OL,8,Fprevious mechanisms introduced
OL,9,Funilaterally by the last UK government.
OL,11,FThe new framework, which includes
OL,12,Fcommitments to fundamentally reform
OL,13,Fthe mechanisms established in the 2023
OL,14,FLegacy Act, has raised expectations
OL,15,Fthat the Irish Government is moving
OL,16,Fcloser to dropping its interstate
OL,17,Flegal case against the UK.
