OL,3,CWhat does the new Troubles legacy
OL,4,Cframework include?
OL,6,FMr Harris said his Government would
OL,7,F"revisit" its stance on the legal
OL,8,Faction if the legislative commitments
OL,9,Flaid out in the framework are
OL,10,Ffaithfully implemented.
OL,12,FLabour came to power with a pledge to
OL,13,Freplace and repeal the 2023 Legacy Act
OL,14,Fintroduced by the Conservatives, which
OL,15,Fhalted scores of civil cases and
OL,16,Finquests into Troubles deaths.
