OL,3,CWhat does the new Troubles legacy
OL,4,Cframework include?
OL,6,FThe Act was opposed by victims' groups
OL,7,Fand political parties in Northern
OL,8,FIreland, and it led the Dublin
OL,9,FGovernment to launch an interstate
OL,10,Flegal case against the UK, claiming it
OL,11,Fbreached the European Convention on
OL,12,FHuman Rights (ECHR).
OL,14,FThe legislation created a new legacy
OL,15,Fbody, the Independent Commission for
OL,16,FReconciliation and Information
OL,17,FRecovery (ICRIR), to take over the
OL,18,Finvestigation of all outstanding
OL,19,FTroubles cases.
