OL,3,CWhat does the new Troubles legacy
OL,4,Cframework include?
OL,6,FThe Act also contained an offer of
OL,7,Fconditional immunity to some suspects
OL,8,Fbut this was disapplied after legal
OL,9,Faction by bereaved families.
OL,11,FThe new framework is closer to the
OL,12,Fdetails of the Stormont House
OL,13,FAgreement of 2014, which were never
OL,14,Fimplemented.
OL,16,FIt will see the ICRIR fundamentally
OL,17,Freformed to become a Legacy
OL,18,FCommission, which will investigate
OL,19,FTroubles deaths.
