OL,3,CWhat does the new Troubles legacy
OL,4,Cframework include?
OL,6,FMr Harris said the joint agreement had
OL,7,Fcreated a moment of "imperfect
OL,8,Fopportunity" and urged victims and
OL,9,Fsurvivors to consider supporting the
OL,10,Fproposals.
OL,12,FThe framework will require new
OL,13,Flegislation at both Westminster and at
OL,14,Fthe Dail.
OL,16,FBoth governments have carried out
OL,17,Fconsultation with victims' groups and
OL,18,Ffamilies and will continue to do so
OL,19,Fonce the framework is published.
